OL,5, Broadcaster Nicky Campbell has revealed
OL,6, for the first time that he was the     
OL,7, victim of abuse at a private school in 
OL,8, Edinburgh during the 1970s.            
OL,10,FThe 61-year-old told his BBC Sounds    
OL,11,Fpodcast Different he witnessed and     
OL,12,Fexperienced sexual and violent physical
OL,13,Fabuse at the Edinburgh Academy.        
OL,15,FHe told BBC Radio 5 Live the abuse had 
OL,16,Fa "profound effect on my life" and had 
OL,17,Fbeen "obsessing me".                   
OL,19,FThe Academy "wholeheartedly" apologised
OL,20,Fand said it had helped police.         
